::Firearm::

Firearm throws himself to the ground, two missiles flying over him. He jumps 
to his feet, frowning as he sees a missile coming out of nowhere, hitting him 
in the side. Firearm stumbles forward, his side shooting sparks.

Transforming to tank mode once again, the Maximal drives at where he saw the 
missile come out of, firing his missile launcher at BumbleBee.

"Let's get out of here!" he says into his comm-link to the other Maximals 
there.
